            <title>[LOG4J2-1488] (GC) %date conversion pattern with a period &apos;.&apos; is not garbage free</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-1488</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The garbage free documentation states that &quot;millisecond separator may be either a comma &apos;,&apos; or a period &apos;.&apos;&quot; but when using a period the garbage free FixedDateFormat is not used.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
